		"description": "<div class=\"grid_8 omega posts righter\">\n<div id=\"block-ipress-content\" class=\"mbf clearfix blockcontent\">\n<article class=\"magic-item full clearfix\" role=\"article\" data-history-node-id=\"2989\">\n<div class=\"name\">\n<div class=\"magic-item-page-header\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-field-mi-description field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--item\">\n<p>None living know who or what Dal was, only that the name is carved into this device. About half a foot in diameter, this flat disk resembles a sundial with many styles (time-telling edges), each of which can be moved on its own course, rotating on the flat of the disc on an undetectable groove. As these are moved, you receive a vision of events and emotions that have occurred in your current location.</p>\n<p>As an action, you can use the dial of Dal to cast the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.24rmiwo0w5pd746x]{Legend Lore} spell focused on your current location without the need for material components. Once used in this way, the dial cannot be used again until you finish a <span class=\"freelinking-link\">long rest</span>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n</div>",
